<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَلَوْ كَشَفَتْ الأَجْدَاثِ مُعْتَبِرًا لَهُمْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لِيَنْظُرَ آثَار الْبَلَى كَيْفَ يَصْنَعُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَشَاهَدَ أَحْدَاقًا تَسِيلُ وَأَوْجُهًا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مُعَفَّرَة فِي التُّرْبِ شُوْهًا تَفْزِّعُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>غَدَتْ تَحْتَ أَطْبَاقِِ الثَّرَى مُكْفَهِرَّةً<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>عَبُوسًا وَقَدْ كَانَتْ مِنْ الْبِشْرِ تَلْمَعُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَلَمْ يَعْرَف الْمَوْلَى مِنَ الْعَبْدِ فِيهِمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَلا خَامِلاً مَنْ نَابِهِ يَتَرَفَّعُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَأَنَّى لَهُ عِلْمٌ بِذَلِكَ بَعْدَمَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَبَيَّنَ مِنْهُمْ مَا لَهُ الْعَيْن تَدْمَعُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>رَأَى مَا يَسُوءُ الطَّرْف مِنْهُمْ وَطَالَمَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>رَأَى مَا يَسُرُّ النَّاظِرِينَ وَيَمْتِعُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>رَأَى أَعْظُمًا لا تَسْتَطِيعَ تَمَاسُكَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تَهَافَتْ مِنْ أَوْصَالِهَا وَتَقَطَّعُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>مُجَرَّدَةً مِنْ لَحْمِهَا فَهِيَ عِبْرَةٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>لِذِي فِكْرَةٍ فِيمَا لَهُ يَتَوَقَعُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>تَخُونُهَا مَرَّ اللَّيَالِي فَأَصْبَحَتْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَنَابِيبَ مِنْ أَجْوَافِهَا الرِّيحُ تُسْمَعُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>إِلَى حَالَةٍ مُسَوَّدَةٌ وَجَمَاجِمٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مُطَأْطَأَةٍ مِنْ ذِلَّةٍ لَيْسَ تَرْفَعُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أُزِيلَتْ عَنِ الأَعْنَاقِ فَهِيَ نَوَاكِسٌ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>عَلَى التُّرَابِ مِنْ بَعْدِ الْوَسَائِدِ تُوضَعُ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>جج<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>